title: Thailand Thai Overnight Repurchase Rate (THOR)
description: Thailand Thai Overnight Repurchase Rate (THOR) was at 0.99 percent on Thursday November 10. Repo Rate in Thailand averaged 0.54 percent from 2020 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 0.99 percent in September of 2022 and a record low of 0.48 percent in October of 2020. In Thailand, the THOR Rate refers to the interbank rate overnight private repurchase rate. This page includes a chart with historical data for Thailand THOR.
author: Bank of Thailand
